ze: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;拉丁裔选民帮助特朗普&lt;/strong&gt;在 2024 年重新掌权，他们可能是他&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/KbqhnClsUS-rVBYwCRmTHvGdoX57vtMWiJXrucDA1p_rX_J2zEpUhvkBKG2pPHwLmSkpg3pu0le-QaOt8sg0yYu5Y0h1dB6e4QeJ94euwEt5jG5PO4dYf2ngbXf4IldgiElljk50D_70OecRSC6jsqRfyV2fpQnpoXylOYbWWCSiGpPCJlH-8t5BP520VcOxBRFxnBIx8XtU7_bBcb8QdQwHk7nn19_st9kpotEbvCKxpOHoU6SE8URP5YF28SM9KdjWjKbJFKAva3YCCO-H0xIL2wz7x3ZoVm4fvEUAX4cdPZhZLlH4iSzV0zcXX_cTxg8Q4U0URlbz8yQP1H9AmKls_Lk0ab-Ql5pwDWQCcdk50XcMTNoz4PqWPg5mRq7qASFwLgt0CBVnVvZR7chXSP0oQyQnJkjq6bmgwLcGs4iFCfQ3kCp4kGpNmlH4Krjcc2JLzt1lIb08wpKCAm2dxuuaxqSwnRvbXwMm9Ni_UZLNRYvQHZKkX7b-RSQ8zakdNfQ2h-Zbs-ELWM8/WaE4zxQb69FZA6BwK466SBHHlMfULslK/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="共和党在中期选举前面临失去拉丁裔支持的风险"&gt;失去众议院甚至参议院控制权的&lt;/a&gt;原因。根据佛罗里达大西洋大学为彭博新闻社进行的一项全国性独家民意调查，在特朗普担任第二任总统一年多后，经济、通胀和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/lfcEb77ivavHsSExo2AhXy6i8docyLqzN7U9yWf1kc8z86phLE7jrTqRoVtK-XeEYSzyVGjf-yhoQCNWhdLDDp-UJfMbB9zp8CdeVXEfLH_UV0ERiX5Yrig1Qj47uEAuHuq7hYVN4RWpqAyU-akLTC4a70jUpsRZUxwDneWAMonkNNb5hjVxdEbTH3KuDwswV98GybOEonS3tmV60zJTLAyb7OERlUWb83QXz4l6xOyYXlcqKfnTu0g3Zlhzhrr7Wv2JOWlbzV1zGJUmgA-XvwnLvfM7A5UmbqjFzmW5MBqYNVNBUy_QzOHiuumespxvEreHt2b6wZPsHmZ5gJhY_YY8Sp7jdNmM9NUOSykkv9SGlsIo6ghmswp0LUyg_ZOt7DVbA3xm4SmYk5VNjLjDCZ4BVGaNz1nO66uI7HZPtGdbWiundL8O6zb_NU537HCYL1oqsGGSAGLFLDNsO3lNzbIhfM7kro1CV4ze2Be7-tKJ8WjmMHoLzTwi0WwDPhITA2-6RCBD_Plp/JK20OztekT0U4r-CDsVYXjXIK8fPZmpA/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普的移民镇压并没有促进美国出生工人的就业"&gt;移民&lt;/a&gt;等问题，在 11 月&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/RQ323KWEJ8HIbNs3AsFzp59U7qdlP6zl6hX93Zu3WVqmTJD8oJxH0FDrNM6Ebm5iWjTeu6ZDDmMMX4oO5Qx3_rubXeu3u1VSNBjJC13d369kV6xChhg7fd0XeFLB-mVvwAuHZCv9Yra9kijvmKHgFUvV7eh3gSToG1Az-sKzwgAb9NH3bEhFQKwjOjIrYW0QuAQ8WHvg4oAbph2znqNDVanW-Havvj2aWoG3qUNBXSt36TSeoWJrhmYACcO9UWdiqYtmF81ioj50lK6nwRUvbFV-N